<unit id="6bb1e0f7-1830-4b4d-b627-2b96e189b9ed">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 4</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Author(s) : Abdel, Rémy, Abdellah zineddine, Jean-François COLAS.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="7fe450b3-aef0-4239-a842-98020d8e9d42">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 6</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix: # </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Presentation #</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="9ce1b91c-df34-49a9-9eb2-ad1a69c19d19">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 8</note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>This add-on improves the accessibility of the software mp3DirectCut with NVDA.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="9aafc51d-520d-4342-a134-5e6d87d64ee3">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 10</note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>It has been tested with versions of mp3DirectCut ranging from 212 up to 233.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="c7c41bb6-65c7-4051-aae5-ec20e956d271">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 12</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix: ## </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Keyboard shortcuts ##</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="57b5ada1-0a8a-4dcb-b11e-02a314573ad1">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 14</note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>This addon offers the following commands:</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="784d1047-e603-4ae1-a45c-1bc70404877f">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 16</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>B</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="31d51de0-1b7f-44cc-8931-938fad4225b8">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 18</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix:     * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Used to confirm correct placement of the marker of the beginning of the selection B.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="6d740b88-1d4b-4452-8345-be94fb4766fb">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 20</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Ctrl+Shift+B</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="77a8851c-23d7-4348-af99-87490cd0cfc5">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 22</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix:     * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Used to indicate the position of the marker of the beginning of selection B.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="15d5d527-2129-46ca-87d1-dc00832a9eb4">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 23</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix:     * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Double pressure lets give you the duration of the selection.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="0d344c04-6cdc-48a1-bee5-5583ed5cfa89">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 25</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Ctrl+Shift+D</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="7ac6a745-4519-421f-a022-a79e2926e241">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 27</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix:     * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Gives the duration from the beginning of the file to the current position of the playback cursor.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="85d69d3e-3f7d-4424-ad1e-c1221209a574">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 28</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix:     * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Double pressure lets give you the total duration.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="3eb47558-7419-4432-84e9-7531d9a8f077">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 30</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Ctrl+R</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="c8f34d55-2a7c-4679-9c7e-24018ff81ac0">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 32</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix:     * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Confirms that the selection has been canceled.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="41251e66-93b8-4cb4-b834-6882c8dee1ea">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 34</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Ctrl+Shift+R</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="2af33010-1b7a-431b-9294-44c99bd807a6">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 36</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix:     * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Gives the time remaining from the current position of the playback cursor to the end of the file.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="ab4d924a-0731-4ae9-9547-327803433db6">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 38</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Ctrl+Shift+E</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="65fc61a2-5cd9-47c4-bea3-aeb24c4a3da7">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 40</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix:     * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Used to indicate the position of the marker of the end of selection N.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="066fe64d-51fe-4d6d-b4c4-aaaf9a5ec429">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 41</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix:     * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Double pressure gives recapitulatif positions B and N, and the duration of the selection.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="40285bb2-3f77-46f9-9df5-bed836f993bb">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 43</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Ctrl+Shift+P</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="0853888c-1458-4340-89b8-232d6cf493e0">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 45</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix:     * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Give the reference of the actual part and the total number of parts in the current file.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="561340d8-2b6e-4aeb-bd7a-cadfad7d06b7">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 47</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Ctrl+Shift+Space</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="04c813d2-00d2-4f78-8b59-3c9d3ed289f1">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 49</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix:     * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Used to determine the current level of the vu-meter, during recording.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="ff48f8e5-cc58-4560-b58c-c8ebb9f30976">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 50</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix:     * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Double pressure reset it.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="bf819f1c-81f8-4a99-af19-df0915c50874">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 52</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Down Arrow</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="869d8dc1-2c5a-48f1-92f0-f70c94d68fa4">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 54</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix:     * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>Lets you see the current position of the playhead.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="ca5dbdf7-79da-43ef-9178-46e5c66f26ab">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 55</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix:     * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>This command also position the cursor at the location of the marker of the end of selection N, while giving the location of this marker if a selection has been made.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="fb48ef47-9d8a-4002-8039-5041e2badaa5">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 56</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix:     * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>In the volume dialog box, vocalise the next value that can be reached generally with downArrow.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="374146e0-e5f6-4707-93cf-5312c3ad3e3f">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 57</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix:     * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>This value is not vocalized default.</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="21204286-1d1a-40e0-b08b-947f207bec5b">
<notes>
<note appliesTo="source">line: 59</note>
<note appliesTo="source">prefix: * </note>
</notes>
<segment>
<source>End</source>
</segment>
</unit>
<unit id="a4a4890b-8bc7-46e8-b9f8-f6d1cedff681">
